            bedrooms, large living area, infinity pool, garden, air conditioned
            gym, professional pool table, BBQ and Sala, this villa is perfect
            for up to 14 adults with 260sqm (2798sqfeet) of living space and
            260sqm of outdoor space.
          </p>
        </div>
